msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.43:0.2"
msgid "5. Akkosavagga"
msgstr "5. Abuse"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.43:0.3"
msgid "43. Dutiyavivādamūlasutta"
msgstr "43. Roots of Arguments (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli5.79"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an10.43:1.1"
msgid "“Kati nu kho, bhante, vivādamūlānī”ti?"
msgstr "“Sir, how many roots of arguments are there?”"

msgctxt "an10.43:1.2"
msgid "“Dasa kho, upāli, vivādamūlāni."
msgstr "“Upāli, there are ten roots of arguments."

msgctxt "an10.43:1.3"
msgid "Katamāni dasa?"
msgstr "What ten?"

msgctxt "an10.43:1.4"
msgid ""
"Idhupāli, bhikkhū anāpattiṃ āpattīti dīpenti, āpattiṃ anāpattīti dīpenti, "
"lahukaṃ āpattiṃ garukāpattīti dīpenti, garukaṃ āpattiṃ lahukāpattīti "
"dīpenti, duṭṭhullaṃ āpattiṃ aduṭṭhullāpattīti dīpenti, aduṭṭhullaṃ āpattiṃ "
"duṭṭhullāpattīti dīpenti, sāvasesaṃ āpattiṃ anavasesāpattīti dīpenti, "
"anavasesaṃ āpattiṃ sāvasesāpattīti dīpenti, sappaṭikammaṃ āpattiṃ "
"appaṭikammāpattīti dīpenti, appaṭikammaṃ āpattiṃ sappaṭikammāpattīti dīpenti."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant explains what is not an offense as an offense, and "
"what is an offense as not an offense. They explain a light offense as a "
"serious offense, and a serious offense as a light offense. They explain an "
"offense committed with corrupt intention as an offense not committed with "
"corrupt intention, and an offense not committed with corrupt intention as an "
"offense committed with corrupt intention. They explain an offense requiring "
"rehabilitation as an offense not requiring rehabilitation, and an offense "
"not requiring rehabilitation as an offense requiring rehabilitation. They "
"explain an offense with redress as an offense without redress, and an "
"offense without redress as an offense with redress."

msgctxt "an10.43:1.5"
msgid "Imāni kho, upāli, dasa vivādamūlānī”ti."
msgstr "These are the ten roots of arguments.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.43:1.6"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
